Jab 2.notes: Transitions to Jab 3 as early as frame 6

Up Smash.notes: Head Invulnerability on frame 9-12. Charge hold is frame 6.

Neutral Air.notes: Auto cancels on frame 1-2 and frame 39 onward.

Forward Air.notes: Auto cancels on frame 1-2 and frame 43 onward.

Back Air.notes: Auto cancels on frame 1-5 and frame 19 onward.

Down Air.notes: Auto cancels on frame 1-4 and frame 33 onward.

Up B (Super Jump Punch).notes: Invulnerable on frame 3-6. Hits 2-6 rehit rate of 2.

Down B (F.L.U.D.D.).notes: Startup is 2 from a charging state. Entering charge state takes 19 frames and is shield cancellable on 20.

Down B, Fully Charged (F.L.U.D.D.).notes: Takes 100 frames to reach full charge.

Jab 1.notes: Transitions to Jab 2 as early as frame 8.

Forward Smash.notes: Arm and head intangibility on frame 20-26. Charge hold is frame 14. Cannot rebound.

Up Smash.notes: Arm and head intangibility on frame 12-15. Charge hold is frame 6. Cannot rebound.

Down Smash.notes: Arm intangibility on frame 11-14. Charge hold is frame 2. Cannot rebound.

Up Air.notes: Head intangibility on frame 5-10. Autocancels on frame 1-5 and 26 onward

Neutral B (Giant Punch).notes: Entering charge window takes 7 frames. 4 to cancel with shield. Arm intangibility on frame 4-20. Cannot rebound.

Giant Punch, Full Charge.notes: Ground version has Super Armor frames 11-20. Air version has Super Armor frames 17-20. Takes 121 frames to reach full charge. Cannot rebound.

Side B (Headbutt).notes: Super armor on frame 5-14 on the ground and in the air.

Up B (Spinning Kong).notes: Super armor on frame 5-17. Arm intangibility on frame 19-24

Spinning Kong, Air.notes: Past frame 12, this move hits once every 1, 2, or 3 frames, seems inconsistent. Arm intangibility from frame 10-38

Down B (Hand Slap).notes: Each additional rep takes another 26 frames as you mash.

Jab 1.notes: Transitions to Jab 2 as early as frame 12

Jab 2.notes: Transitions to Jab 3 as early as frame 8.

Forward Tilt.notes: Hits targets above him on frame 15

Forward Smash 1.notes: Transitions to second swing as early as frame 22. Sword Sword Beam is active 17-48 when at minimum charge and 17-56 when at maximum charge (only when Link is at 0%). Charge hold frame is 9.

Down Air.notes: Autocancels on frame 1-9 and 65 onward. Can hit same target once again after 30 frames due to pogo effect.

Neutral B (Hero's Bow).notes: Reaches full charge on frame 52. Arrows travel for 46 frames after being fired. Arrows will stick into the ground for 3 seconds and can be picked up to either item-throw or fire two arrows. When firing two arrows at once, the second one generates three frames after the first.

Side B (Boomerang).notes: 9 frame animation of catching boomerang if no other action is being performed.

Up B (Spin Attack).notes: Can charge attack for an additional 60 frames. Startup is 4 from charge state. 7f startup is only the front hit.

Jab 1.notes: Transitions to Jab 2 as early as frame 15.

Forward Smash.notes: Deals 1.0 more damage when angled up, 1.0 less when angled down. Charge hold frame is 3.

Neutral B (Charge Shot).notes: Startup is 3 from charge state. Takes 13 frames to enter charge state.

Charge Shot, Full Charge.notes: Takes 125 frames to reach full charge

Side B (Homing Missle).notes: Projectile lasts until frame 118. Total frames is 59 in the air for either missile type.

Side B (Super Missle).notes: Projectile lasts until frame 87. Starts moving forward around frame 50, allowing for followups.

Up B (Screw Attack).notes: Invulnerable on frame 3-6. Rehit rate of 6 for active frames 7-24.

Up B, Air (Screw Attack, Air).notes: Invulnerable on frame 3-4. Rehit rate of 2 for all hits except final.

Down B (Bomb).notes: Bomb is generated on frame 11. Explosion occurs one frame after touching a target. Bomb explodes automatically on frame 83. Total frames is 44 if the player is holding down.  And 48 in the air with no way to reduce it.
